<template>
  <v-container fluid class="down-top-padding">
    <BaseBreadcrumb :title="page.title" :icon="page.icon" :breadcrumbs="breadcrumbs"></BaseBreadcrumb>
    <v-row>
      <v-col cols="12" sm="12">
        <BaseCard heading="Expansion panels - Disabled">
          <ExpansionDisabled></ExpansionDisabled>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Expansion panels - Readonly">
          <ExpansionReadonly></ExpansionReadonly>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Expansion panels - Popout">
          <ExpansionPopout></ExpansionPopout>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Expansion panels - Inset">
          <ExpansionInset></ExpansionInset>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Expansion panels - Accordion">
          <ExpansionAccordion></ExpansionAccordion>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Expansion panels - Focusable">
          <ExpansionFocusable></ExpansionFocusable>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Expansion panels - External control">
          <ExpansionExternalControl></ExpansionExternalControl>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Expansion panels - Custom icon">
          <ExpansionCustomicon></ExpansionCustomicon>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Expansion panels - Advanced">
          <ExpansionAdvanced></ExpansionAdvanced>
        </BaseCard>
      </v-col>
    </v-row>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "Expansionpanels",

  data: () => ({
    page: {
      title: "Expansion panel"
    },
    breadcrumbs: [
      {
        text: "UI Components",
        disabled: false,
        to: "#"
      },
      {
        text: "Expansion panel",
        disabled: true
      }
    ]
  }),
  components: {
    ExpansionDisabled: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/expansionpanel/ExpansionDisabled"),
    ExpansionReadonly: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/expansionpanel/ExpansionReadonly"),
    ExpansionPopout: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/expansionpanel/ExpansionPopout"),
    ExpansionInset: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/expansionpanel/ExpansionInset"),
    ExpansionAccordion: () =>
      import(
        "@/components/vuetifyComponents/expansionpanel/ExpansionAccordion"
      ),
    ExpansionFocusable: () =>
      import(
        "@/components/vuetifyComponents/expansionpanel/ExpansionFocusable"
      ),
    ExpansionExternalControl: () =>
      import(
        "@/components/vuetifyComponents/expansionpanel/ExpansionExternalControl"
      ),
    ExpansionCustomicon: () =>
      import(
        "@/components/vuetifyComponents/expansionpanel/ExpansionCustomicon"
      ),
    ExpansionAdvanced: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/expansionpanel/ExpansionAdvanced")
  }
};
</script>
